161→
162→            // rqd is currently not able to report exit_signal=9 when a frame is killed by
163→            // the OOM logic. The current solution sets exitStatus to
164→            // Dispatcher.EXIT_STATUS_MEMORY_FAILURE before killing the frame, this enables
